===b. Send and receive by semaphore code at the rate of seven words per minute using semaphore flags. (Five-letter words, minimum of 20 words.)=== {{:Adventist Youth Honors Answer Book/Semaphore Code}} ===c. Send and receive by International Morse Code at the rate of three words per minute using wigwag flags. (Five-letter words, minimum of 20 words.)=== {{:Adventist Youth Honors Answer Book/Wigwag Code}}
