== Diff style ==

Hello, we have noticed that after the [[mw:MediaWiki 1.20/wmf1|deployment of MediaWiki 1.20wmf1]] an old local customised diff style has not been removed from this page. 1.20 brings a new, greatly improved diff style which is no longer compatible with older customisations. To prevent the new release from worsening rather than improving your diffs, a global interface editor has agreed to help you by removing the old code in a week from now unless you object. You'll then be able to see if the new style suits you or needs a new customisation. I hope this helps, [[User:Nemo bis|Nemo bis]] ([[User talk:Nemo bis|discuss]] • [[Special:Contributions/Nemo bis|contribs]]) 20:54, 5 August 2012 (UTC)
